    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College Job offer placement was also good",
          "name": "MOHAMMAD ZAFAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Crowd was good, Ground was quite big to spend time, Special Place - Jannat",
          "name": "Konark",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Wi-Fi facilities was also good for the students",
          "name": "Konark",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Well-structured courses equipped with relevant knowledge and skills.",
          "name": "Gagandeep Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "library is one of the finest in campus of du",
          "name": "krishna gupta",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College societies are very active. Engaging and unique events and competitions are held with exciting rewards, such as case hunts. Society specific seminars are held with successful, diligent speakers time-to-time",
          "name": "Kanishk Tailwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good sponsorship engagement of societies with events and free refreshments",
          "name": "Kanishk Tailwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The social life at Sgtb khalsa is very active , with a wide range of society and events , including fests like Lashkara which seeks participation from a huge number of students.",
          "name": "Rakshita",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty is also very well educated and have gained expertise in their areas of study. The faculty is collaborative as well , they do cooperate with students by understanding their needs and problems.",
          "name": "Rakshita",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College admission process, like the teachers are supportive and all . They help you with various growing skills and ideas for further carrier development",
          "name": "Priyanshu Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Fees was still high in comparison to other colleges, and in comparison to infrastructure, it was indeed high",
          "name": "Konark",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Occasionally, there are some administrative inefficiencies.",
          "name": "Gagandeep Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "library closes at 6pm should give more time",
          "name": "krishna gupta",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lots of writing work such as assignments, tests, etc. which may not provide any value addition",
          "name": "Kanishk Tailwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Language subject in each semester, English in alternative semesters and Hindi in each semester",
          "name": "Kanishk Tailwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement opportunities are not that good , it could be improved more .",
          "name": "Priyanshu Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Internship opportunities are also kot that good like in paid terms the amount provided is not that good.",
          "name": "Priyanshu Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "My college does provide placements as well but relatively less alluring than some other top colleges",
          "name": "Anudit singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure of the college is not very good as compared to other north campus colleges.",
          "name": "Rahul Kumar Keshri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College gym is only accessible to people coming from sports background.",
          "name": "NIRVIKA",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Delhi University, New Delhi"
    }
